title: Chris Mazdzer, Usain Bolt, and a guide to the Winter Youth Olympic Games in Lausanne
description: We’ve all the info you need for the start of Lausanne 2020... There's a good luck message from eight-time Olympic champion Usain Bolt, a walk through the historic St Moritz track with Olympic silver medallist Chris Mazdzer, and much more...
